data.description: Step into comfort at this charming 3 bed, 1 bath Miami home. Spanning 936 sq ft on a generous 7,900 sq ft lot, this residence radiates warmth with its baby blue paint. Enjoy the fenced backyard, perfect for leisure and featuring a custom outdoor grill, covered patio, and a handy storage shed. Inside, the bathroom's tasteful updates add modern flair. Rest easy under a new roof (2021) and stay cool with the newly installed A/C system. Impact windows ensure security and efficiency. Conveniently located near the Turnpike, Coral Reef Drive, and Zoo Miami, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. A must-see!
